ments: mean large\nseparation, variation of the large separation with frequency, small separation\nand degree identification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2009 13:08:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2009 10:03:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2009 10:47:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
