time function implies stable causality, and a new short proof of\nthe equivalence between K-causality and stable causality is given which takes\nadvantage of Levin's theorem and smoothing techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2009 13:35:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-23"}
